Subject: [PATCH 1/2] feat(runner): add port_listening assertion type
 (FEAT-004)

Adds PortCheck struct to schema with port, protocol, and host fields.
CheckPortListening dials the address with 5s timeout, defaults to
tcp/localhost. Wired into runner assertion evaluation. Test covers
failure case on closed port.
